Titolo: NBA Courtside 2 Featuring Kobe Bryant

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: NBA Courtside 2 Featuring Kobe Bryant is a basketball video game developed by Left Field Productions and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo 64. The game was released in North America exclusively in 1999. It is the sequel to Kobe Bryant in NBA Courtside and features NBA star Kobe Bryant on its cover. Bryant also performed the motion capture for the game.A Game Boy Color version of the game was released at the same time, entitled NBA 3 on 3 Featuring Kobe Bryant.
The third and final edition in the Courtside series, NBA Courtside 2002 was released for the GameCube in 2002.